item.title: Oscar Aydin Infiltrates the Mile High Club
item.description: Oscar Aydin (Netflix, Bravo) is a gut-busting standup comedian who complains so joyfully, you’ll pay to hear it, but today he’s in the apartment to complain about airplanes not keeping enough NUTS stocked for SUCKING! We discuss joining the mile high club under the cover of a medical emergency, fleeing muscle-bound ex-boyfriends who hunt you down for your hookups, and the secrets to organizing a gay movement (that targets Krispy Kreme). Ashley is glowing up. Kylie is puking... Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/werehavinggaysex
